<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200729/5ecbb96c146e4d15ab3a464449f01b6d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>人物档案：诗人马文峰： 70后中国青年诗人、百网联盟融媒体矩阵链创始人、延安365公益协会顾问团顾问、延安陕北青年创业联合会名誉会长、陕西省筑梦春天志愿者协会荣誉会长、西安市德钰堂助医公益慈善基金会监事长、陕西省山东菏泽商会宣传总顾问、94版央视三国演义关羽扮演者，《一壶老酒》原唱陆树铭先生陆家班策划总顾问，宣传总顾问、陕西广播电视台《秦之声》文化旅游产业联盟副秘书长、延安市总工会、延安市文明办、延安市教育局、共青团延安市委、延安市工商联合会、延安市残疾人联合会、陕西省宋庆龄基金会延安分会、延安市妇女联合会学雷锋公益爱心大使、西安市文史研究院研究员、西安市模特艺术学会宣传策划总顾问</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《延安颂》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">潺潺延河水，巍巍宝塔山。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">圣地杨家岭，又见枣园前。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">峥嵘岁月远，理想信念坚。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">艰难凝众智，军民渡难关。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两万五千里，辗转到延安。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凤凰迎红日，领袖在田间。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">切切如在耳，难忘南泥湾。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">俯首英魂在，历历皆可观。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抗大育英雄，奋斗创新天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">精神朝圣地，家国负双肩。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红旗不褪色，长治又久安。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天公重抖擞，振兴谱史篇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 《中国魂》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">南湖红船启初航，百战生死写史章。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不忘初心度风雨，山河锦绣享荣光。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《军魂》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">八一军旗迎风扬，烈士血撒历沧桑。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">气贯长虹军歌亮，丹心碧血洗国殇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">华夏儿女当自强，盛世中华铸辉煌。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">科技强军放光芒，东方文明永留芳。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《山河赋》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">马踏飞燕观沧海，梦卧白云听雨潺。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仙游九州江海阔，笑傲江湖天地间。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来时青山隐绿水，书中自有千万卷。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红尘三千挂心间，脚踏五岳醉碧川。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《人民子弟兵》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">八一军歌声嘹亮，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">保家卫国铁嵴梁。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抗洪救灾展风骨，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甘撒热血军姿壮。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万里河山凛然气，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赤胆碧心身戎装。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">军令如山赴战场，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正气浩然万世芳。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《天问一号》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天际一箭向苍穹，屈子问道始征程。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鲲鹏展翅向云庭，文昌飞天赴火星。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">金蝉声鸣烟阙咏，银河作赋醉仙聆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">中华儿女齐欢腾，捷报传来气恢弘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 《百花 》 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 人间仙境百花舍，清风伴月几人歌。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 化为笔墨写青史，挥洒春秋染山河。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《企业家精神》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">热血浇灌中华地，艰苦创业来兴邦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">策马扬鞭奔康庄，建功立业谱华章。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《东北黑土地》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">革命先贤勇拓荒，广袤无际变粮仓。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">黑土地中稻花香，五谷丰登诗韵藏。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三江河畔秀锦妆，意气风发盛世昌。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">华夏江山千万里，人和业兴日月长。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《闽宁镇》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">昔日戈壁滩，今日绿色天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">脱贫致富时，黄沙变良田。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闽宁时光迁，特色经济颜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">扶贫又扶智，荒滩变庄园。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日暖熏幽径，花草逸香甜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">致富来勤勉，绿洲迎贺兰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">帮扶典范田，催马奋扬鞭。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诗词赋天地，喜报迎向前。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《听雨亭》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闲情信步听雨亭，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">竹林通幽不染尘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">七月荷塘谢花雨，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">柳青倒影染暮晨。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诗书长醉红尘路，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">韶华逝水岁如风。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">几声雀声惊闲梦，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来日仙踪上九重。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《夏荷》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文\文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">湖池琼蕊伞盈香，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">露迎珠莹衬红妆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仙姿清丽秀霓裳，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">潋滟碧色映星光。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">嫣然一笑处何方，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">亭亭玉立秀水乡。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">东坡盼尔墨韵舱，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">踏波仙子赋芬芳。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《茶赋》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">半阙诗词境悠远 ，一壶清醇韵味长。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">茶能醉君不需酒，书能香我何须花。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为品清香频入座，清茗一杯情更深。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">四海皆来求知客，谈笑鸿儒现故人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《文殊菩萨》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">八千佛莲入红尘，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">智慧普渡赋众生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">七窍莲花菩提中，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">莫叹柳絮知人声。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花开笑面见佛性，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">妙法莲花慈悲经。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">芙蓉出水禅心静。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《曲江南湖》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">曲江池水碧色芳，南湖秀木沐霞光。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把盏吟赋草木香，佳人对饮话诗章。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">光景满天飞花畅，湖岸垂髫锦鲤忙。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">芦苇丛中画意妆，留恋忘返不思乡。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(南湖南栖小院)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《高考》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">十年寒窗图自强，心怀励志求学榜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">海阔任由群鲤跃，金科题名慰悬梁。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《笔墨人生》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夏有凉风冬听雪，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">春有百花秋望月。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">岁寒三友真君子，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">耐性显能凭精神。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">读书随笔知迷津，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万物造化皆乾坤。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">洞见红尘留后世，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">逍遥自在观浮沉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《曲江》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">曲江美景画中来，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">翠色入水几时裁。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流云唤醒唐宋句，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">琴瑟和鸣绕玉台。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《文昌国运》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一轮明月诗情少，半阙书心送君迟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 本是九天宫廷客，却因清茶恋红尘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">千里清风万里路，几度烟雨几度嗔。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 花开叶落终有时，文昌再度有缘人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《人间路》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人间词曲苍茫路，借问君去与谁行。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三千弱水终有尽，春归故里唯有情。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《诗情》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">高朋挚友喜迎春，天涯美景共良辰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长空碧水犹诗梦，灯耀他乡未归人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《夏荷》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">碧水池中万朵莲，清风徐来韵荷田。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">绿颜伴红醉世间，红尘最美六月天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《友谊》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">胸中存笔墨，下笔诗自成。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">明月送友谊，不及鲁朝情。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《荷赋》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文/文峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">荷叶团团暖风香，芙蓉出泥着新装。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">阅尽人间红尘客，化为若水福瑞长。</p>